<%= form_for(project) do |f| %>
  <%= f.label :name %>
  <%= f.text_field :name %>
  <%= f.label :description %>
  <%= f.text_area :description %>
  <%= f.datetime_field :due_date %>
  A group project? Select your group here:
  <%= f.collection_select :team_id, current_user.teams.all, :id, :name, {:include_blank => true} %>
  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>


LOGIC:

either it's an individual project
- use user_id
or it's a group project:
- user team_id
